EQualized scoring: Everyone gets 100 PPT and no PPH or yellow bonus. There is a small bonus for number of taken zones during a month (max 8000 zones). It does not matter if you lose your zones. No disadvantage in towns with high turf activity and low PPT. Unfairness that still remains - uneven distribution of zones.
